#2-%E5%AE%BD%E5%BA%A6%EF%BC%9Agrid-template-columns%E3%80%81grid-template-rows"><span class="toc-number">11.2.2.</span> <span class="toc-text">2.宽度：grid-template-columns、grid-template-rows</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#3-%E9%97%B4%E9%9A%94%EF%BC%9Agrid-gap-%EF%BC%88grid-row-gap-grid-column-gap-%EF%BC%89"><span class="toc-number">11.2.3.</span> <span class="toc-text">3. 间隔：grid-gap （grid-row-gap +grid-column-gap ）</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#4-%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%E5%8C%BA%E5%9F%9F%EF%BC%9Agrid-template-areas"><span class="toc-number">11.2.4.</span> <span class="toc-text">4.定义区域：grid-template-areas</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#5-%E6%8E%92%E5%88%97%E9%A1%BA%E5%BA%8F%EF%BC%9Agrid-auto-flow"><span class="toc-number">11.2.5.</span> <span class="toc-text">5.排列顺序：grid-auto-flow</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#6-%E5%8D%95%E5%85%83%E6%A0%BC%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%E4%BD%8D%E7%BD%AE%EF%BC%9Aplace-items-%EF%BC%88justify-items-align-items%EF%BC%89"><span class="toc-number">11.2.6.</span> <span class="toc-text">6.单元格内容位置：place-items （justify-items + align-items）</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#7-justify-content-%E3%80%81-align-content-%E3%80%81-place-content"><span class="toc-number">11.2.7.</span> <span class="toc-text">7.justify-content 、 align-content 、 place-content</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#8-grid-auto-columns-%E3%80%81-grid-auto-rows"><span class="toc-number">11.2.8.</span> <span class="toc-text">8.grid-auto-columns 、 grid-auto-rows</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#9-grid-template-%E3%80%81grid"><span class="toc-number">11.2.9.</span> <span class="toc-text">9.grid-template 、grid</span></a></li></ol></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-2"><a class="toc-link" href="#item%E5%B1%9E%E6%80%A7"><span class="toc-number">11.3.</span> <span class="toc-text">item属性</span></a><ol class="toc-child"><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#1-grid-column-start-%E5%B1%9E%E6%80%A7%EF%BC%8C-grid-column-end-%E5%B1%9E%E6%80%A7%EF%BC%8C-grid-row-start-%E5%B1%9E%E6%80%A7%EF%BC%8C-grid-row-end-%E5%B1%9E%E6%80%A7"><span class="toc-number">11.3.1.</span> <span class="toc-text">1.grid-column-start 属性， grid-column-end 属性， grid-row-start 属性， grid-row-end 属性</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#2-grid-column-%E5%B1%9E%E6%80%A7%EF%BC%8C-grid-row-%E5%B1%9E%E6%80%A7"><span class="toc-number">11.3.2.</span> <span class="toc-text">2.grid-column 属性， grid-row 属性</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#3-grid-area-%E5%B1%9E%E6%80%A7"><span class="toc-number">11.3.3.</span> <span class="toc-text">3.grid-area 属性</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#4-justify-self-%E5%B1%9E%E6%80%A7%EF%BC%8C-align-self-%E5%B1%9E%E6%80%A7%EF%BC%8C-place-self-%E5%B1%9E%E6%80%A7"><span class="toc-number">11.3.4.</span> <span class="toc-text">4.justify-self 属性， align-self 属性， place-self 属性</span></a></li></ol></li></ol></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-1"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E8%AF%B4%E8%AF%B4%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0%E5%A4%9A%E7%AB%AF%E9%80%82%E9%85%8D%EF%BC%9F"><span class="toc-number">12.</span> <span class="toc-text">说说如何实现多端适配？</span></a><ol class="toc-child"><li class="toc-item toc-level-2"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E7%99%BE%E5%88%86%E6%AF%94%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%EF%BC%9F%E2%9D%8C"><span class="toc-number">12.1.</span> <span class="toc-text">百分比布局？❌</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-2"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E7%BA%AFvw-vh%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%EF%BC%9A%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E7%A0%96%E5%9D%97%E2%9D%8C"><span class="toc-number">12.2.</span> <span class="toc-text">纯vw+vh方案：智能砖块❌</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-2"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E5%AA%92%E4%BD%93%E6%9F%A5%E8%AF%A2-rem%EF%BC%9F%E2%9D%8C"><span class="toc-number">12.3.</span> <span class="toc-text">媒体查询+rem？❌</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-2"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E5%AA%92%E4%BD%93%E6%9F%A5%E8%AF%A2-rem-viewport-calc"><span class="toc-number">12.4.</span> <span class="toc-text">媒体查询+rem+viewport+calc()</span></a></li></ol></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-1"><a class="toc-link" href="#1px%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98"><span class="toc-number">13.</span> <span class="toc-text">1px问题</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-1"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E5%8F%82%E8%80%83%E9%93%BE%E6%8E%A5"><span class="toc-number">14.</span> <span class="toc-text">参考链接</span></a></li></ol>
